Nicole Kidman, 55, was the epitome of glamour as she modelled Balenciaga at Paris Fashion Week. The Australian beauty walked the runway for the fashion brand alongside A-listers such as Kim Kardashian, Dua Lipa and Bella Hadid.Nicole wowed fans once again when she returned to her hotel room and posed for a series of sultry shots.The Big Little Lies star posed on her bed wearing a shimmering black dress. In a separate post, she could also be seen posing in an elevator and strolling through The Peninsula’s corridors.Her Instagram followers were amazed by the photos, including @stedfast_productions who said: “You are the most beautiful lady as always.”Hunter added: “Queen of Balenciaga!”And Ramona said: “Paris is even more amazing with you there.”